{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I've got shoes, and men's suits, thinking I'm going to see Freddy whenever, whether it's one day, or one week, or one month, and then he's got something to put on his back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, unfortunately, I never saw him again, but that's beside the point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I took that suitcase, and with that suitcase, I followed the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went first to the house where the family was, in the Jewish star house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody was there yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I was walking towards the ghetto, I met Grandma, my auntie, and her little daughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, we fell into each other's arms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, where's Freddy?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, we haven't seen him since two days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One and a half days ago he was with us, and then he went back to that place where he's sleeping.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to go there now, straightaway , and get him and come over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, you can't visualize what it is like, a war-torn city, where, on the electrical wires where the trams were going, there was a body there, and the head here, and the leg there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was snowing, and in the snow was red.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And horses were dead, and it was absolutely a dreadful sight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you see your family, certain paths, to see each other, you don't see anything of that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You only see it after or before, but you, you-- at that second, it was only the hugging, that we survived it, and we are here and the Russians--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Grandma and Auntie went into the star house, and I went opposite direction, to the ghetto, to look for my brother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said they haven't seen him the last day and a half.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, oh shit.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
